Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.01,0:22:11.64,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}无法入眠的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:15.10,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}独自一人叹息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.85,0:22:18.52,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}大家又如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.31,0:22:22.44,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}总觉得很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.73,0:22:28.78,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}广阔的大地上 一粒种子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.53,0:22:31.91,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}伸展开根系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.12,0:22:39.75,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}又结出青色的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.87,0:22:44.55,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想要早些成为橙色的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.55,0:22:47.76,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}沐浴着你的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:51.39,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}理想和梦想不断膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.39,0:22:54.64,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}快察觉到吧 呐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.89,0:22:58.23,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今天也品尝了橙子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:23:01.56,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}依然酸涩 不禁落泪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:05.07,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不能让它像我一样被丢弃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.07,0:23:07.61,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}全部吃完了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.61,0:23:14.03,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}喜欢你哦 要哭了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.45,0:23:21.04,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}喜欢你哦 喜欢你哦
